@host = https://localhost:44319

### Validation - invalid job application id
POST {{host}}/api/application-events
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "jobApplicationId": 0,
  "eventType": 0,
  "eventDate": "2026-06-07",
  "note": "Invalid job application id"
}

### Validation - too long note
POST {{host}}/api/application-events
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "jobApplicationId": 1,
  "eventType": 0,
  "eventDate": "2026-06-07",
  "note": ""
}

### Business validation - job application not found
POST {{host}}/api/application-events
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "jobApplicationId": 999,
  "eventType": 0,
  "eventDate": "2026-06-07",
  "note": "Should return 404 from custom exception"
}